Package pdfrecompression

Class Summary
Jbig2ForPdf class representing list of images compressed according to JBIG2 standard in format suitable for pdf and byte array of global Data
PdfImage class representing JBIG2 image in format suitable for pdf (without header,...)
PdfImageInformation Contains information about size of image and it's position in original PDF
PdfImageProcessor This will read a pdf and extract images (names of images are stored in list and put back their compressed version)
PdfObjId Represents PDF object identifier
Run  
Tools  
 

Exception Summary
PdfRecompressionException Thrown when found problem with recompressing PDF file
